title: Winning numbers drawn in 'Cash 5' game
maintext:
AUSTIN, Texas (AP) _ The winning numbers in Monday evening’s drawing of the Texas Lottery’s “Cash 5” game were:
03-04-11-13-35
(three, four, eleven, thirteen, thirty-five)
